casebody.data:
Sinclair A. PARKER, Jr.
v.
Michael WILLIS. No. 54P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 6, 2005. Stephen C. Baynard, Wilmington, for N.C. Farm Bureau Mutual. Maynard M. Brown, Wilmington, for Michael Willis. Richard A. Mu, Jacksonville, for Sinclair A. Parker, Jr.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 24th day of January 2005 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of April 2005."
